ht;\"> 0.03 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.07 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n`````\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Updated since publication (through the latest survey year)\n\nOn the full monitoring record, the common-broadcaster cover half-life is **15 years** at TCRMP, **26** at VINPS, and **26** at CSUN. The three-way interaction reads p = 0.003 at VINPS, p = 0.049 at CSUN, and p = 0.078 at TCRMP. Within brooders, the Year x Rarity interaction reads p < 0.001 at VINPS, p = 0.001 at CSUN, and p = 0.378 at TCRMP. Across TCRMP and VINPS, **16 of 41** baseline species were lost by the most recent period (39%), and CSUN lost **4 of 17** genera (24%). The octocoral study window now runs 2014 to 2024, a span of 10 years. These numbers differ from the published section because the range extends past 2023.\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n`````{=html}\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"width: auto !important; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n<caption>Per-program headline statistics (updated).</caption>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Program </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> Common-broadcaster % / yr </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p (slope) </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> Cover half-life (yr) </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> Three-way p </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> Within-brooder Year x Rarity p </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> TCRMP </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> -4.6 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> p &lt; 0.001 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 15 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> p = 0.078 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> p = 0.378 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> VINPS </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> -2.6 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> p = 0.002 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:r